  "texts": [
    "The following schema (Fig. 5) illustrates this idea using an example.",
    "According to this strategy, a further embedding called \"Vocab_type\" could be added to the other inputs, including the semantics of each vocabulary to the final embedding.",
    "However, this approach generates an overload of information in the final embedding.",
    "Thus, we must evaluate the real predictive value of the embeddings to eliminate or represent them differently.",
    "Table 2 shows that most approaches use the same positional encoding principles to provide the notion of position (or order) to input tokens."
